# Demand

A JavaScript solution for creating your own CDN for all of your JS code. A work in progress project.

## Demo
Would you like to check out the latest version? All you have to do is to copy the following tag into the `head` section of your website:

```html
<script type="text/javascript" src="http://asec.github.io/demand/demo/demand.min.js"></script>
```
After that you can invoke the power of `demand` simply by writing something like this:

```javascript
demand("bootstrap.3", function(){

	jQuery(document).on("ready", function(){
		alert("This page now has jQuery and bootstrap support. Pretty neat huh? :)");
	});

});
```
